{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d07a1bb4fa","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cf3fdafc92","index":0,"year":1955,"month":3,"day":14,"articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"87860d9449","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指黄炎培1955年3月11日给毛泽东的信。信中向毛泽东报告了中国民主建国会将于4月1日召开全国代表大会的准备情况，信后附有他对失业问题和农村粮食问题的意见。关于农村粮食问题，信中说：最近有人从家乡来，反映一般居民生活苦，尤其是农民特别苦，农民说：我们吃不饱，哪有力气去种田呢？而一些村干部工作作风不好，总疑心农民家有藏粮，致使民间有忽声。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7e7ee27af2","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"87860d9449","type":"paragraph","text":"任之先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"65282efb71","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十一日惠书收读。民建开代表大会，很好，谨致祝贺。农村粮食问题已采取措施，下一年度可以缓和下来，目前则仍有些","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"7ba29a83c4","type":"subtitle","text":"紧张。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"682c954ae5","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"bfabe51d94","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"d8f7021955","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年三月十四日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"},{"id":"025852c5e8","type":"paragraph","text":"口黄炎培，字任之，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、全国人大常委会副委员长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d07a1bb4fa"}],"page":{"id":"21703